name: Te Vejo Na Pista - 1
description:
final take from my video TE VEJO NA PISTA and the most beautiful and inspiring kiss I have ever seen. TE VEJO NA PISTA was initiated with this clip, captured by @caveiradepraia at some Masterplano party,  back in 2019 when everything was normal and we didn't dream about being only in-home, without parties. 

dedicated to all lovers who dare to kiss on the dance floor.
mixed technique, digital painting, textured cell phone video
